{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":148704,"duration_api_ms":147823,"num_turns":14,"result":"","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"9c3e95e2-9c98-46fa-9097-e94442d82b97","total_cost_usd":0.6304985,"usage":{"input_tokens":11,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29375,"cache_read_input_tokens":273297,"output_tokens":2535,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":29375,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":11,"outputTokens":2535,"cacheReadInputTokens":273297,"cacheCreationInputTokens":29375,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.38367225,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":106,"outputTokens":8482,"cacheReadInputTokens":1269690,"cacheCreationInputTokens":61873,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.24682625,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"structured_output":{"amendments":[],"summary":"The implementation is well-structured and correct. The change extracts inline `RecordProducer::Agent` construction into a shared `agent_record_producer()` helper that derives `backend_family` and `model_id` from `InvocationEnvelope.metadata` (specifically `backend_used.family` and `model_used.model_id`). The helper is applied consistently across all four call-sites: `engine.rs` (main stage invocation), `completion.rs` (completer panel), `final_review.rs` (reviewer/voter/arbiter invocations), and `prompt_review.rs` (refiner/validator invocations). Each inner `invoke_*` function now returns `(Value, RecordProducer)` instead of just `Value`, capturing producer metadata at the point where the envelope is available rather than reconstructing it from the resolved target. The conformance test was tightened to assert specific `backend_family` and `model_id` values. A unit test covers the helper. No remaining inline `RecordProducer::Agent` construction exists in production code. No amendments needed."},"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"80d7c201-d404-4830-8cd3-83dd820b1e18"}
